WEBVTT

00:00:30.492 --> 00:00:34.612
an advantageous location that makes
trade and administration possible;

00:00:34.636 --> 00:00:36.828
the potential for scalable opportunities

00:00:36.852 --> 00:00:39.229
for the skilled and unskilled alike;

00:00:39.253 --> 00:00:42.272
a popular willingness
to be in constant flux

00:00:42.296 --> 00:00:44.049
and, of course, resilience.

00:00:44.767 --> 00:00:47.598
The "how" of cities, however,
is a whole other story.

00:00:48.175 --> 00:00:49.878
How are they run?

00:00:49.902 --> 00:00:51.695
How do they grow?

00:00:51.719 --> 00:00:54.597
How do they decide who belongs
and who doesn't?

00:00:55.751 --> 00:00:57.529
Lagos is my home.

00:00:58.540 --> 00:01:00.211
You can always find the Nigerians